      "id": "b891364887a4919a",
      "text": "A core element of the assessment system is ​__continuous two-level peer review__​. This novel peer-review model addresses weaknesses of existing peer-review and allows us to more accurately curate knowledge and technology and assess its quality. Continuous two-level peer review is a ​direct assessment​ of a contribution.\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "ef00e137-e4a2-439e-8e54-5fff31e6c6fc",
